    "content": "DUA ALLAHUMMA ASLEH\r\n\r\n--بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ اَللّٰهُمَّ أَصْلِحْ عَبْدَكَ وَ خَلِیْفَتَكْ بِمَا أَصْلَحْتَ بِهِ اَنْبِیَآءَكَ وَ رُسُلَكْ، وَ حُفَّهُ بِمَلَآئِكَتِكْ، وَاَیِّدْهُ بِرُوْحِ الْقُدْسِ مِنْ عِنْدِكْ وَ اسْلُكْهُ مِنْ بَیْنِ یَدَیْهِ وَ مِنْ خَلْفِهِ رَصَدًا یَحْفَظُوْنَهُ مِنْ كُلِّ سُوْءٍ، وَ اَبْدِلْهُ مِنْ بَعْدِ خَوْفِهِ اَمْنًا یَعْبُدُكَ لَا یُشْرِكُ بِكَ شَیْئًا، وَ لَا تَجْعَلْ لِاَحَدٍ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ عَلٰی وَلِیِّكَ سُلْطَانًا وَاْذَنْ لَهُ فِی جِهَادِ عَدُوِّكَ وَ عَدُوِّهْ، وَ اجْعَلْنِی مِنْ اَنْصَارِهْ اِنَّكَ عَلٰی كُلِّ شَیْ‏ءٍ قَدِیْرٍ۔", 
    "audio": "http://www.ya-mahdi.net/apps_audio/alahomaasleh.mp3", 
    "transliteration": "DUA ALLAHUMMA ASLEH\r\n\r\nBISMILLAHIR RAHMANIR RAHEEM ALLAHUMMA ASLEH A'BDAKA WA KHALEEFATAKA BEMA ASLAHTA BEHI ANBIYAA'AKA WA RUSULAKA WA HUFFAHU BEMALAA'IKATIKA WA AYYID-HO BEROOHIL-QUDUS MIN 'INDEKA WASLUK-HO MIN BAYNE YADAYHE WA MIN KHALFEHI RASADA, YAHFADHOONAHU MIN KULLE SOO'IN WA ABDILHO MIN BA'DE KHAUFEHI AMANA, YA'BODOKA LA YUSHREKU BEKA SHAY'AA, WA LA TAJ'AL LE'AHADIN MIN KHALQIKA 'ALA WALIYYEKA SULTAANA, WA'DHAN LAHOO FI JEHAADE 'ADUWWEKA WA ADOOWWEHI, WAJ'ALANI MIN ANSAAREHI INNAKA 'ALAA KULLE SHAY'IN QADEER.", 
    "english": "DUA ALLAHUMMA ASLEH\r\n\r\nO Allah! Reform conditions of Your servant and caliph with those means by which You have reformed conditions of Your messengers and prophets. Surround him with the angels and support him with the Holy Spirit. Appoint protectors from the front and behind him, (those) who would guard him from all troubles and calamities. Convert his fear into security, (so that) he may worship only You and doesn't associate anybody with You. Do not make any of Your creatures an authority over Your vicegerent. Permit him to fight against Your enemies and his enemies and include me among his helpers. Surely You possess power over everything."
